import {
    
    Container,
    Form,
    FormControl,
    Nav,
    Navbar,
    NavDropdown,
  } from "react-bootstrap";

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="primary" expand="lg" variant="dark">
        <Container>
    <Navbar.Brand>
      <Link to="/">   Â©IMS-INSTITUTE</Link>
      
   </Navbar.Brand>
    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">

        <Nav className="m-auto">
        <Form inline>
          <FormControl type="text" placeholder="search" classname="mr-sm-2" />
          
      </Form>


        </Nav>


      <Nav className="me-auto">
        <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link href="#link">My Courses</Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link href="#link">My Classes</Nav.Link>
        <NavDropdown title="S.Amarasinghe" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">My Profile</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Log Out</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Genarate Report</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Divider />
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Separated link</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>
      </Nav>
      
    </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Container>
</Navbar>
    );
};

export default Header;
